sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as kuberay-operator<br/>Controller Manager
    participant Scheduler as K8s Scheduler
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379,8265,10001/TCP
    participant WorkerPod as Ray Worker Pod
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + Service<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Scheduler->>Registry: Pull Ray Image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Pull Secrets
    Registry-->>Scheduler: Ray Container Image
    Scheduler->>HeadPod: Start Ray Head<br/>GCS + Dashboard
    Scheduler->>WorkerPod: Start Ray Workers
    WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Register with GCS<br/>Ray Protocol/6379<br/>Optional mTLS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster for Job<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job Submitter Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount
    Scheduler->>Registry: Pull Job Image
    Registry-->>Scheduler: Job Container
    Scheduler->>HeadPod: Submit Ray Task<br/>gRPC/10001 Optional TLS<br/>Optional Token Auth
    HeadPod->>WorkerPod: Distribute Work<br/>Ray Protocol/6379<br/>Optional mTLS
    WorkerPod->>S3: Save Results<br/>HTTPS/443 Cloud IAM

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Ray Serve Inference
    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayService CR<br/>Bearer Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster + Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Ingress/Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    User->>HeadPod: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/8000<br/>Optional Bearer Token
    HeadPod->>WorkerPod: Inference Request<br/>Ray Protocol Optional TLS
    WorkerPod->>S3: Load Model<br/>HTTPS/443 Cloud IAM
    S3-->>WorkerPod: Model Artifacts
    WorkerPod-->>HeadPod: Prediction Result
    HeadPod-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    User->>HeadPod: View Dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265 Optional TLS
    HeadPod-->>User: Cluster Metrics UI
    User->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
    Operator-->>User: Prometheus Metrics
